OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FSunshine and
OL,6,Fblustery showers continuing this
OL,7,Fevening. Clearer spells developing
OL,8,Fovernight as showers remain mainly to
OL,9,Fthe west of the Pennines but remaining
OL,10,Fwindy with strong gusts.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FA dry start to the day with
OL,13,Fpatchy cloud around but remaining
OL,14,Fbreezy. Showers developing from later
OL,15,Fmorning but these less heavy than
OL,16,Fprevious days. The wind gradually
OL,17,Feases.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
