OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FThe
OL,6,Fweekend is set to be unsettled with
OL,7,Ffurther rain and remaining windy.
OL,8,FDrier on Monday with prolonged sunny
OL,9,Fspells and the wind easing.
OL,10,FTemperatures around average for June.
